# Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and
# files generated by popular Visual Studio add-ons.

## Ignore Visual Studio user-specific files
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Ignore build output
bin/
obj/
out/
AppPackages/
*.nupkg
*.snupkg

## Ignore NuGet package directories
packages/
!packages/repositories.config

## Ignore .NET Core & .NET 5+ generated files
project.lock.json
project.assets.json
artifacts/

## Ignore logs and database files
*.log
logs/
*.mdf
*.ldf

## Ignore Rider and VS Code files
.idea/
*.code-workspace
.vscode/

## Ignore JetBrains Rider
*.sln.iml

## Ignore Resharper
*.DotSettings.user

## Ignore temp files
*.tmp
*.bak
~*

## Ignore publish directory
publish/
wwwroot/dist/
wwwroot/node_modules/

## Ignore secrets and credentials
secrets.json
appsettings.Development.json
